      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STAGE 'N' SCREEN (2) continues to race well and will take a power of beating again. A narrow win three back has preceded two close up placings, beaten as favourite here last time but perhaps unsuited in the small field there. This trip is an unknown but she's bred to run it and if anything it could spark further improvement. GREY ICE (3) made nice improvement second up going to 1600m behind a subsequent Group 2 placegetter in Mystery 'N' Drama. Up in trip here should suit much better and she can prove hard to hold out. EN FLIQUE (4) is racing well, winning two of her past three. This is harder but she can measure up. SEAFALL (1) drops in grade off some even runs of late and could be an improver while LUVYA MUMMA (8) is going well without winning and has claims again.",
